LG.L:
þer he set at his biede 128, 4 dahinter sind zwei strophen ausgefallen, die in T 267 bis 270 so lauten:



þo, þe was oðer mannes þing

leuere, þan hit solde,

and waren al to gradi

of siluer and of golde;




þo, þe untrewnesse deden þan,

þe he solden ben holde,

and leten al, þat hie solden don,

and deden, þat hie wolden;
;
